      <title>中国外长表示北京和雅加达希望地区和平与稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-says-beijing-jakarta-want-regional-peace-stability-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部长王毅周四在雅加达与印度尼西亚外长蕾特诺·马尔苏迪举行会谈后表示，中国和印度尼西亚希望维护该地区的和平与稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-says-beijing-jakarta-want-regional-peace-stability-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，韩国 LG 电子计划通过美元债券筹集至多 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-lg-electronics-plans-raise-up-1-bln-with-dollar-bonds-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位直接了解此事的消息人士透露，韩国 LG 电子公司计划通过美元债券交易筹集至多 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-koreas-lg-electronics-plans-raise-up-1-bln-with-dollar-bonds-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称加强与日本和美国关系的决定是“主权选择”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-says-decision-strengthen-ties-with-japan-us-sovereign-choice-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾外交部周四表示，菲律宾加强与日本和美国关系的决定是“主权选择”，并敦促中国“反思自己在南海的行为”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-says-decision-strengthen-ties-with-japan-us-sovereign-choice-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>悉尼邦迪韦斯特菲尔德购物中心在致命刺伤事件后重新开放以示悼念</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sydneys-bondi-westfield-mall-reopens-tributes-after-fatal-stabbings-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[悉尼邦迪韦斯特菲尔德购物中心周四重新开放，这是自周六一名男子持刀杀死六人后警方开枪射杀他以来首次重新开放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sydneys-bondi-westfield-mall-reopens-tributes-after-fatal-stabbings-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元暂停飙升，亚洲股市涨跌互现</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，亚洲股市涨跌互现，小幅走高，美元稍作喘息，债券市场企稳，投资者开始评估利率前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 02:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚3月就业情况令人失望，失业率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-march-employment-unexpectedly-falls-6600-jobless-rate-ticks-up-38-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚就业人数在前一个月大幅增长后出现下降，同时失业率恢复上升趋势，这表明相对紧张的劳动力市场仍有望放松，尽管速度较慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-march-employment-unexpectedly-falls-6600-jobless-rate-ticks-up-38-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者思考美国利率前景，美元稍作喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-takes-breather-investors-ponder-us-rates-outlook-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四美元走软，因美联储官员发表评论后交易员评估了美国利率前景，这些言论巩固了货币环境在一段时间内仍将保持限制性的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-takes-breather-investors-ponder-us-rates-outlook-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:36:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AI芯片需求强劲，台积电第一季度利润将增长5%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-5-rise-first-quarter-profit-strong-ai-chip-demand-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台积电是人工智能应用先进芯片的主要生产商，由于需求强劲，预计周四第一季度利润将增长 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-5-rise-first-quarter-profit-strong-ai-chip-demand-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:31:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国市场监管机构敦促公司认真听取股东的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/skorea-market-watchdog-urges-companies-listen-carefully-shareholders-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融监管机构负责人周四表示，公司应更加关注股东的声音，因为政府寻求通过改革鼓励更高的股东回报来提振国内股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/skorea-market-watchdog-urges-companies-listen-carefully-shareholders-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
